summary: AFTER OWNING THE VEHICLE FOR JUST TWO MONTHS, WHILE DRIVING ON THE HIGHWAY A SMALL PARTICLE STRUCK THE WINDSHIELD AND MADE A CHIP THE SIZE OF A NICKEL.  A FEW MILES DOWN THE HIGHWAY THE SAME INCIDENT HAPPENED MAKING A CRACK THAT IS SPIDERING THE SIZE OF A HALF DOLLAR.  SPOKE WITH THE KIA DEALER TO REPORT THE ISSUE.  THEY DO NOT HAVE ANY WINDSHIELD RECALLS AT THIS TIME.
